forecasts for 1989 and 1990. The figures were provided by the
London investment firm Barclays de Zoete Wedd Ltd.:
   1985 _ 3.9 percent
   1986 _ 3.2 percent
   1987 _ 4.5 percent
   1988 _ 4.3 percent
   1989 _ 2 percent
   1990 _ 1 percent
