   Standard &amp; Poor's industrial index fell 2.33 to 407.40, and
S&amp;P's 500-stock composite index was down 2.14 at 356.99.
   The NASDAQ composite index for the over-the-counter market
slumped 1.98 to 482.16. At the American Stock Exchange, the market
value index closed at 395.68, down 1.35.
